{
  "video_id": "itLUXZnLRn8",
  "title": "The next generation of African architects and designers | Christian Benimana",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 15651.0,
      "text": "The longest journey that I have ever taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16470.0,
      "end_time": 18314.0,
      "text": "That was in 2002."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18869.0,
      "end_time": 20298.0,
      "text": "I was only 19 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21146.0,
      "end_time": 24475.0,
      "text": "It was the first time I had ever been on an airplane"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24499.0,
      "end_time": 27304.0,
      "text": "and the first time that I had left my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27328.0,
      "end_time": 28477.0,
      "text": "Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29423.0,
      "end_time": 32613.0,
      "text": "I had to move thousands of kilometers away"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32637.0,
      "end_time": 33918.0,
      "text": "to follow a dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34262.0,
      "end_time": 37274.0,
      "text": "A dream I have had ever since I was a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37889.0,
      "end_time": 41862.0,
      "text": "And that dream was to become an architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43264.0,
      "end_time": 45865.0,
      "text": "That was impossible at the time in my country."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45889.0,
      "end_time": 47720.0,
      "text": "There were no schools of architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48426.0,
      "end_time": 51487.0,
      "text": "So when I got a scholarship to study in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51511.0,
      "end_time": 54217.0,
      "text": "I left my life and my family behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54241.0,
      "end_time": 56820.0,
      "text": "and I moved to Shanghai."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56724.0,
      "end_time": 58741.0,
      "text": "It was an amazing time."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59252.0,
      "end_time": 63579.0,
      "text": "This country was going through a major building boom."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63603.0,
      "end_time": 65385.0,
      "text": "Shanghai, my new home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65410.0,
      "end_time": 67952.0,
      "text": "was quickly turning into a skyscraper city."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69241.0,
      "end_time": 70935.0,
      "text": "China was changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70959.0,
      "end_time": 75395.0,
      "text": "World-class projects were built to convey a new image of development."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75889.0,
      "end_time": 81579.0,
      "text": "Modern, striking engineering marvels were going up literally everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82493.0,
      "end_time": 85187.0,
      "text": "But behind these facades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85212.0,
      "end_time": 89434.0,
      "text": "exploitation of huge numbers of migrant workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89458.0,
      "end_time": 92615.0,
      "text": "massive displacement of thousands of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92639.0,
      "end_time": 94661.0,
      "text": "made these projects possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95420.0,
      "end_time": 96968.0,
      "text": "And this fast-paced development"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96992.0,
      "end_time": 99979.0,
      "text": "also contributed significantly to the pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100300.0,
      "end_time": 101639.0,
      "text": "that is haunting China today."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102758.0,
      "end_time": 104696.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward to 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104720.0,
      "end_time": 106848.0,
      "text": "when I went back home to Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107320.0,
      "end_time": 111571.0,
      "text": "There, I found development patterns similar to what I saw in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112870.0,
      "end_time": 118590.0,
      "text": "The country was and still is experiencing its own population and economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118574.0,
      "end_time": 121749.0,
      "text": "The pressure to build cities, infrastructure and buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121773.0,
      "end_time": 123669.0,
      "text": "is at its peak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123693.0,
      "end_time": 124914.0,
      "text": "and as a result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124939.0,
      "end_time": 127342.0,
      "text": "there is a massive building boom as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128392.0,
      "end_time": 133266.0,
      "text": "This is the reality across the entire continent of Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133290.0,
      "end_time": 134440.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s why."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134913.0,
      "end_time": 138210.0,
      "text": "By 2050, Africa&#39;s population will double,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138450.0,
      "end_time": 141531.0,
      "text": "reaching 2.5 billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142323.0,
      "end_time": 143935.0,
      "text": "At this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143959.0,
      "end_time": 148990.0,
      "text": "the African population will be slightly less than the current population"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149140.0,
      "end_time": 153156.0,
      "text": "of China and India combined."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154963.0,
      "end_time": 159932.0,
      "text": "The infrastructure and buildings needed to accommodate this many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159956.0,
      "end_time": 163491.0,
      "text": "is unprecedented in the history of humankind."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164720.0,
      "end_time": 167410.0,
      "text": "We have estimated that by 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167434.0,
      "end_time": 172652.0,
      "text": "we have to build 700,000,000 more housing units,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172676.0,
      "end_time": 175664.0,
      "text": "more than 300,000 schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 175688.0,
      "end_time": 179677.0,
      "text": "and nearly 100,000 health centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 181173.0,
      "end_time": 183840.0,
      "text": "Let me put that into perspective for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 184902.0,
      "end_time": 188583.0,
      "text": "Every day for the next 35 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 188608.0,
      "end_time": 191521.0,
      "text": "we have to build seven health centers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191545.0,
      "end_time": 193403.0,
      "text": "25 schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 193427.0,
      "end_time": 198129.0,
      "text": "and nearly 60,000 housing units each day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 198153.0,
      "end_time": 199442.0,
      "text": "every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 202390.0,
      "end_time": 204911.0,
      "text": "How are we going to build all of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 205698.0,
      "end_time": 210550.0,
      "text": "Are we going to follow a model of unsustainable building and construction"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 210790.0,
      "end_time": 212295.0,
      "text": "similar to what I witnessed in China?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 212319.0,
      "end_time": 216351.0,
      "text": "Or can we develop a uniquely African model"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216376.0,
      "end_time": 219448.0,
      "text": "of sustainable and equitable development?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 219905.0,
      "end_time": 221594.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m optimistic we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 221992.0,
      "end_time": 224560.0,
      "text": "I know Africans who are already doing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225334.0,
      "end_time": 228374.0,
      "text": "Take Nigerian architect Kunlé Adeyemi for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 228398.0,
      "end_time": 231635.0,
      "text": "and his work in slums of coastal megacities."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 232121.0,
      "end_time": 235420.0,
      "text": "Places like Makoko in Lagos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235660.0,
      "end_time": 239827.0,
      "text": "where hundreds of thousands of people live in makeshift structures on stilts"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239851.0,
      "end_time": 241280.0,
      "text": "on water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241520.0,
      "end_time": 243459.0,
      "text": "without government infrastructure or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244272.0,
      "end_time": 249841.0,
      "text": "A community at great risk of rising sea levels and climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 250223.0,
      "end_time": 254576.0,
      "text": "And yet, people who live here are examples of great ingenuity"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 254600.0,
      "end_time": 256620.0,
      "text": "and the will to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 256644.0,
      "end_time": 259719.0,
      "text": "Kunlé and his team have designed a prototype school"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259744.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262713.0,
      "text": "that is resilient to rising sea levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 262737.0,
      "end_time": 264989.0,
      "text": "This is Makoko School."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266502.0,
      "end_time": 270707.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a floating prototype structure that can be adapted to clinics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270731.0,
      "end_time": 273480.0,
      "text": "to housing, to markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273504.0,
      "end_time": 276520.0,
      "text": "and other vital infrastructure this community needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 276760.0,
      "end_time": 278116.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an ingenious solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 278140.0,
      "end_time": 282894.0,
      "text": "that can ensure this community lives safely on the waters of Lagos."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 283895.0,
      "end_time": 285950.0,
      "text": "This is Francis Kéré."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 286726.0,
      "end_time": 288775.0,
      "text": "He works in the country where he comes from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 288799.0,
      "end_time": 289948.0,
      "text": "Burkina Faso."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 290374.0,
      "end_time": 295930.0,
      "text": "Kéré and his team have designed projects that use traditional building techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 296434.0,
      "end_time": 299890.0,
      "text": "Kéré and his team working in the communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 299113.0,
      "end_time": 301934.0,
      "text": "have developed prototype schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 301958.0,
      "end_time": 303450.0,
      "text": "that the whole community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 303474.0,
      "end_time": 307980.0,
      "text": "similar to every project in the villages of this country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 307122.0,
      "end_time": 309100.0,
      "text": "comes together to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 310280.0,
      "end_time": 313110.0,
      "text": "Children bring stones for the foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 313350.0,
      "end_time": 316366.0,
      "text": "women bring water for the brick manufacturing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 316390.0,
      "end_time": 320420.0,
      "text": "and everybody works together to pound the clay floors."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 320946.0,
      "end_time": 322232.0,
      "text": "Working with the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 322256.0,
      "end_time": 325890.0,
      "text": "Kéré and his team have created projects that function better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325915.0,
      "end_time": 328551.0,
      "text": "with adequate lighting and adequate ventilation."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 329231.0,
      "end_time": 332303.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re appropriate for this particular context"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 332327.0,
      "end_time": 334153.0,
      "text": "and really, really beautiful as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334881.0,
      "end_time": 336643.0,
      "text": "For the past seven years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 336668.0,
      "end_time": 340242.0,
      "text": "I have been working as an architect at MASS Design Group."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 340266.0,
      "end_time": 342983.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a design firm that began in Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 344480.0,
      "end_time": 347710.0,
      "text": "We have worked in several countries in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 347734.0,
      "end_time": 352460.0,
      "text": "focusing on this more equitable and sustainable model"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 352710.0,
      "end_time": 353911.0,
      "text": "of architectural practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 353935.0,
      "end_time": 356155.0,
      "text": "and Malawi is one of those countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 356587.0,
      "end_time": 359991.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a country with beautiful, remote landscapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 360150.0,
      "end_time": 362988.0,
      "text": "with high-peak mountains and fertile valleys."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363440.0,
      "end_time": 367455.0,
      "text": "But it also has one of the worst maternal mortality rates in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 369670.0,
      "end_time": 372544.0,
      "text": "A pregnant woman in Malawi either gives birth at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 372568.0,
      "end_time": 376554.0,
      "text": "or she has to walk a really long journey to the nearest clinic."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377535.0,
      "end_time": 382974.0,
      "text": "And one out of 36 of these mothers dies during childbirth."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 384647.0,
      "end_time": 385798.0,
      "text": "In Malawi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 385822.0,
      "end_time": 387712.0,
      "text": "with our team at MASS Design Group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 387736.0,
      "end_time": 390146.0,
      "text": "we designed the Kasungu Maternity Waiting Village."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390856.0,
      "end_time": 394869.0,
      "text": "This is a place women come to six weeks before their due dates."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 395733.0,
      "end_time": 397591.0,
      "text": "Here they receive prenatal care"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 397615.0,
      "end_time": 401510.0,
      "text": "and train in nutrition and family planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 401604.0,
      "end_time": 404171.0,
      "text": "At the same time, they form a community"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 404196.0,
      "end_time": 406715.0,
      "text": "with other expectant mothers and their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 408960.0,
      "end_time": 411484.0,
      "text": "The design of the of Kasungu Maternity Waiting Village"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 411509.0,
      "end_time": 415613.0,
      "text": "borrows from the vernacular typologies of Malawi villages"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 415637.0,
      "end_time": 419840.0,
      "text": "and is built using really simple materials and techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 420230.0,
      "end_time": 425150.0,
      "text": "The earth blocks that we used were made from the same soil of this site."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 425803.0,
      "end_time": 429960.0,
      "text": "This reduces the carbon footprint of this building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 429120.0,
      "end_time": 431191.0,
      "text": "but first and foremost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 431215.0,
      "end_time": 436842.0,
      "text": "it provides a safe and dignified space for these expectant mothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 437361.0,
      "end_time": 440305.0,
      "text": "These examples show that architecture and design"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 440329.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "have the power and the agency to address complex problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 447885.0,
      "end_time": 450617.0,
      "text": "But more to point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 450641.0,
      "end_time": 454338.0,
      "text": "that we can develop a model of effective solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 454362.0,
      "end_time": 455741.0,
      "text": "for our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 456476.0,
      "end_time": 459160.0,
      "text": "But these three examples are not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 460128.0,
      "end_time": 463358.0,
      "text": "300 more examples will not be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 464198.0,
      "end_time": 469556.0,
      "text": "We need a whole community of African architects and designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 469580.0,
      "end_time": 472503.0,
      "text": "to lead with thousands more examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 473182.0,
      "end_time": 475240.0,
      "text": "In May of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 475480.0,
      "end_time": 478619.0,
      "text": "we convened a symposium on African architecture, in Kigali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 478643.0,
      "end_time": 482340.0,
      "text": "and we invited many of the leading African designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 482365.0,
      "end_time": 485984.0,
      "text": "and architectural educators working across the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 486617.0,
      "end_time": 488666.0,
      "text": "We all had one thing in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 490398.0,
      "end_time": 494565.0,
      "text": "Every single one of us went to school abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 494589.0,
      "end_time": 496469.0,
      "text": "and outside of Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 496494.0,
      "end_time": 498810.0,
      "text": "This has to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 499271.0,
      "end_time": 502628.0,
      "text": "If we are to develop solutions unique to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 502652.0,
      "end_time": 506128.0,
      "text": "rather than attempting to turn Kigali into Beijing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 506152.0,
      "end_time": 508637.0,
      "text": "or Lagos into Shenzhen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 508661.0,
      "end_time": 510415.0,
      "text": "we need a community"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 510439.0,
      "end_time": 513764.0,
      "text": "that will build the design confidence of the next generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 513788.0,
      "end_time": 516166.0,
      "text": "of African architects and designers."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 516846.0,
      "end_time": 524316.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 524719.0,
      "end_time": 526310.0,
      "text": "In September last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 526550.0,
      "end_time": 529135.0,
      "text": "we launched the African Design Centre"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 529159.0,
      "end_time": 531864.0,
      "text": "to start building this community."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 533700.0,
      "end_time": 536917.0,
      "text": "We admitted 11 fellows from across the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 538210.0,
      "end_time": 542358.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a 20-month-long, design-build fellowship program."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 543910.0,
      "end_time": 545981.0,
      "text": "Here, they are learning to tackle big challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 546500.0,
      "end_time": 548516.0,
      "text": "such as urbanism and climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 548541.0,
      "end_time": 550320.0,
      "text": "as Kunlé and his team have."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 551367.0,
      "end_time": 552949.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re working with communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 552974.0,
      "end_time": 557580.0,
      "text": "to develop innovative building solutions and processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 557820.0,
      "end_time": 559287.0,
      "text": "as Kéré and his team have."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 560230.0,
      "end_time": 564231.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re learning to understand the health impact of better buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 564255.0,
      "end_time": 567731.0,
      "text": "as we at MASS Design Group have been researching"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 567755.0,
      "end_time": 569361.0,
      "text": "for the past several years."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 569896.0,
      "end_time": 572208.0,
      "text": "The crowning moment of the fellowship"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 572232.0,
      "end_time": 575875.0,
      "text": "is a real project that they designed and built."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 576407.0,
      "end_time": 578924.0,
      "text": "This is Ruhehe Primary School,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 578948.0,
      "end_time": 580406.0,
      "text": "the project they designed."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 580431.0,
      "end_time": 584734.0,
      "text": "They immersed themselves in the community to understand the challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 584758.0,
      "end_time": 587630.0,
      "text": "but also uncover opportunities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 587870.0,
      "end_time": 591218.0,
      "text": "like using a wall made of local volcanic stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 591243.0,
      "end_time": 595320.0,
      "text": "to turn the entire campus into a space of play and active learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 596644.0,
      "end_time": 599490.0,
      "text": "They evaluated the environmental conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 599514.0,
      "end_time": 602768.0,
      "text": "and developed a roof system that maximizes daylight"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 602792.0,
      "end_time": 604850.0,
      "text": "and improves acoustic performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 605243.0,
      "end_time": 609433.0,
      "text": "The construction at Ruhehe Primary School will begin this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 610861.0,
      "end_time": 616735.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 616759.0,
      "end_time": 618243.0,
      "text": "And over the coming months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 618267.0,
      "end_time": 621873.0,
      "text": "the African Design Centre fellows are going to work hand-in-hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 621897.0,
      "end_time": 624434.0,
      "text": "with the Ruhehe community to build it."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 625493.0,
      "end_time": 626736.0,
      "text": "When we asked the fellows"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 626760.0,
      "end_time": 630552.0,
      "text": "what they want to do after their African Design Centre fellowship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 630576.0,
      "end_time": 632835.0,
      "text": "Tshepo from South Africa said"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 632859.0,
      "end_time": 636114.0,
      "text": "he wants to introduce this new way of building into his country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 636138.0,
      "end_time": 639383.0,
      "text": "so he plans to open a private practice in Johannesburg."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 639985.0,
      "end_time": 644238.0,
      "text": "Zani wants to expand opportunities for women to become engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 644966.0,
      "end_time": 647102.0,
      "text": "Before joining the African Design Centre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 647126.0,
      "end_time": 648858.0,
      "text": "she helped start, in Nairobi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 648882.0,
      "end_time": 653573.0,
      "text": "an organization to bridge the gender gaps for women in engineering fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 653597.0,
      "end_time": 656847.0,
      "text": "and she hopes to take this movement across Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 656871.0,
      "end_time": 658448.0,
      "text": "eventually the whole world."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 659574.0,
      "end_time": 662160.0,
      "text": "Moses, from South Sudan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 662410.0,
      "end_time": 664216.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s newest country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 664240.0,
      "end_time": 667232.0,
      "text": "wants to open the first polytechnic school"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 667256.0,
      "end_time": 672280.0,
      "text": "that will teach people how to build using local materials from his country."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 673746.0,
      "end_time": 677244.0,
      "text": "Moses had to be determined to become an architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 678105.0,
      "end_time": 683417.0,
      "text": "The civil war in his country frequently interrupted his architectural education."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 684430.0,
      "end_time": 687786.0,
      "text": "At the time he was applying to join the African Design Centre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 687810.0,
      "end_time": 692501.0,
      "text": "we could hear gunshots going off in the background of his interview call."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 693546.0,
      "end_time": 696872.0,
      "text": "But even in the middle of this civil war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 696896.0,
      "end_time": 698731.0,
      "text": "Moses hangs on to this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 698755.0,
      "end_time": 703781.0,
      "text": "that architecture can be a way to bridge communities back together."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 704727.0,
      "end_time": 708360.0,
      "text": "You have to be inspired by this fellow&#39;s belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 708610.0,
      "end_time": 710585.0,
      "text": "that great architecture can make a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 710609.0,
      "end_time": 713419.0,
      "text": "on how the future of Africa is built."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 714514.0,
      "end_time": 718270.0,
      "text": "The unprecedented growth of Africa cannot be ignored."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 719258.0,
      "end_time": 722881.0,
      "text": "Imagine Africa&#39;s future cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 722905.0,
      "end_time": 725387.0,
      "text": "but not as vast slums,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 725411.0,
      "end_time": 727291.0,
      "text": "but the most resilient"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 727316.0,
      "end_time": 730697.0,
      "text": "and the most socially inclusive places on earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 730721.0,
      "end_time": 732848.0,
      "text": "This is achievable."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 733909.0,
      "end_time": 738280.0,
      "text": "And we have the talent to make it a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 738520.0,
      "end_time": 742390.0,
      "text": "But the journey to ready that talent for the task ahead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 742630.0,
      "end_time": 743730.0,
      "text": "like my own journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 743754.0,
      "end_time": 745000.0,
      "text": "is far too long."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 746674.0,
      "end_time": 751107.0,
      "text": "For the next generation of African creative leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 751131.0,
      "end_time": 754565.0,
      "text": "we have to shorten and streamline that journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 755106.0,
      "end_time": 756492.0,
      "text": "But most importantly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 756516.0,
      "end_time": 758839.0,
      "text": "and I cannot stress this enough --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 758863.0,
      "end_time": 761141.0,
      "text": "we have to build their design confidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 761165.0,
      "end_time": 765358.0,
      "text": "and empower them to develop solutions that are truly African"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 765382.0,
      "end_time": 767593.0,
      "text": "but globally inspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 768820.0,
      "end_time": 769233.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 769257.0,
      "end_time": 776257.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}